Using two blowers: one sucks fresh air in from above the engine ala stock 
aux blower. The other is plumbed into a pipe or hose that draws air from 
inside the bus. One fellow I traded messages with said his drew air from 
the inside of the spare tire well or just behind the side cabinet.

